<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.3">
<l>veḷḷi yāṉkari yāṉmaṇi niṟa vaṇṇaṉ viṇṇavar tamakkiṟai yemak</l>
<l>koḷḷi yāṉuyarn tāṉula kēḻumuṇ ṭumiḻntāṉ</l>
<l>tuḷḷu nīrmoṇṭu koṇṭucā maraik kaṟṟaic cantaṉa muntivan tacai</l>
<l>teḷḷu nīrppuṟa viltiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who is white, he who is dark, the jewel-hued one, lord of the celestials,</l>
<l>The wise one to us, the eminent one, the one who ate the seven worlds</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] disgorged [them],</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr in the forest with clear waters which churn,</l>
<l>Arriving, drawing up leaping waves, tossing up sandalwood</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] clumps of jalap.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
